Legion of Super-Heroes v3 #11
Publisher:  DC Comics
Publication Date:  June 1985

Writers:  Paul Levitz
Penciller:  Ernie Colon and Keith Giffen
Inker:  Larry Mahlstedt and Karl Kesel
Colorist:  Carl Gafford
Letterer:  John Costanza
Cover:  Steve Lightle, Larry Mahlstedt, and Anthony Tollin

The three original Legionnaires, Saturn Girl, Cosmic Boy and Lightning Lad, go to a prison in the Antarctic to view the release of two criminals: the criminals that tried to take the life of R.J. Brande and helped start the Legion of Super-Heroes. The meeting gives the three original members a new perspective in their part of the Legion.

Meanwhile, Superboy talks to Bouncing Boy and considering rejoining the Legion of Super-Heroes, but Bouncing Boy says that he will have stiff competition, telling the story of Comet Queen, a potential candidate.

